  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libkdcraw</title>

    <para>
      <application>Libkdcraw</application> is a KDE wrapper around the
      <xref linkend="libraw"/> library for manipulating image metadata.
    </para>

    &lfs121_checked;

